TITLE: Installing AutoMapper Dependencies with npm
DESCRIPTION: Command to install AutoMapper core, classes strategy, and reflect-metadata using npm.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nartc/mapper/blob/main/packages/documentation/docs/tutorial/create-mapper.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
npm i @automapper/core @automapper/classes reflect-metadata
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Automatic Property Mapping in TypeScript with AutoMapper
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how matching properties are automatically mapped between User and UserDto classes using the @AutoMap() decorator.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nartc/mapper/blob/main/packages/documentations/docs/mapping-configuration/overview.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
class User {
    @AutoMap()
    firstName!: string;
    @AutoMap()
    lastName!: string;
}

class UserDto {
    @AutoMap()
    firstName!: string;
    @AutoMap()
    lastName!: string;
}
```

