TITLE: Initializing Mapper with Classes Strategy in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Creates a new Mapper instance using the classes() strategy initializer. This is the basic setup required to start using AutoMapper.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nartc/mapper/blob/main/packages/documentation/docs/fundamentals/mapper.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const mapper = createMapper({
    strategyInitializer: classes(),
});
```

