TITLE: Creating Main Mapping Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the complete mapping configuration including type conversion, naming conventions, and computed properties.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nartc/mapper/blob/main/packages/documentations/docs/tutorial/mapping-configurations.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
createMap(
    mapper,
    Bio,
    BioDto,
    typeConverter(Date, String, (date) => date.toDateString()),
    namingConventions(new CamelCaseNamingConvention())
);
createMap(
    mapper,
    User,
    UserDto,
    forMember(
        (destination) => destination.fullName,
        mapFrom((source) => source.firstName + ' ' + source.lastName)
    )
);
```

