TITLE: Defining AutoMapper Models in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows the definition of Item, CartItem, and CartItemDto classes with AutoMap decorators for use with AutoMapper.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nartc/mapper/blob/main/packages/documentation/docs/mapping-configuration/for-self.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
class Item {
    @AutoMap()
    name: string;
    @AutoMap()
    price: number;
    @AutoMap()
    stock: number;
}

class CartItem {
    @AutoMap(() => Item)
    item: Item;
    @AutoMap()
    quantity: number;
}

class CartItemDto {
    @AutoMap()
    name: string;
    @AutoMap()
    price: number;
    @AutoMap()
    quantity: number;

    get total() {
        return this.price * this.quantity;
    }
}
```

